{"tid":927913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見國小女童太可愛 男高中生「抱一下」的下場是…","createTime":"2018-12-04T12:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T18:09:52.000Z","uid":35468,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"579c93a670d6e285466810493e716bdd49d50148","tid":927913,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:59:31.000Z","msg":"社會新聞\t<br />\n見國小女童太可愛 男高中生「抱一下」的下場是&hellip;<br />\n2018-12-01 16:37<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n〔記者陳恩惠／台北報導〕台北市劉姓男高中生上個月25日傍晚行經捷運文湖線中山國中站附近，看見2名國小女童玩夾娃娃，很活潑可愛，竟一路尾隨她們，在巷子內攔下2名女童，謊稱學校有「募集擁抱」活動，向她們要簽名，還趁機抱了其中一名女童。女童回到家，將這件事告訴媽媽，台北市警松山分局警方據報，循監視器畫面追緝，前天將劉姓男高校生通知到案，訊後依違反性騷擾防治法及少年事件處理法，將他函送法辦。<br />\n<br />\n女童向警方說，自稱高中生的大哥哥向她們謊稱，學校有「募集擁抱｣活動，要她們幫忙簽名，卻突然抱住她，她嚇得推開，還踢了他一腳，那個高中生說了聲對不起就跑了！<br />\n<br />\n警方調閱監視器畫面發現，高中生犯案後，租了YouBike逃離，根據刷卡紀錄，確認是劉姓高三生；劉姓學生前天在雙親陪同下到案說明，他供稱是因為2名女學生相當可愛，才會做出失禮的行為，事後相當後悔，由於女童家長堅持提告，劉姓學生訊後被依法送辦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2629930_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2629930_1.jpg&h=e16c0ffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉姓高中生與2位國小女童偶遇，見她們長得可愛，竟一路尾隨向她們謊稱學校有「募集擁抱｣活動，不僅要簽名，還趁機抱了其中1女童後離開。（記者陳恩惠翻攝）"},{"pid":"d2b333a8bd922ac5cf0bcd1d705edc90107aeb45","tid":927913,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152f4c114c14fad78e1443a5eaca0b3ba1352b4d","tid":927913,"uid":136002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7fed904b140200d316acca1191410f537a6ae0","tid":927913,"uid":105715,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:10:20.000Z","msg":"小學就著熱褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ec3fc5de2955237944c4d8d99c25bb4b9813b6","tid":927913,"uid":91104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:14:56.000Z","msg":"仲心諗邊個國家叫見國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f2fe46b38739aaa2b623cd88db7dc789fbbe70","tid":927913,"uid":60524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:16:36.000Z","msg":"小學都咁腳長 寶島係有料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db8ff21f5b995664ee1e5d60afe3a35c6de4311","tid":927913,"uid":3189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:25:32.000Z","msg":"台灣啲小學生已經著咁短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寶島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39aebb064981ef2b86410b9705791dbc7b78b80b","tid":927913,"uid":47954,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T15:16:41.000Z","msg":"抱下啫又唔係非禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個男仔應該樣衰所以被metoo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a3bbcc840c520fdbea89d7ac6066b1f819824b","tid":927913,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:09:52.000Z","msg":"有啲生得靚"}]}